&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Measuring Efficiency &amp;amp; Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Usage &amp;amp; Impact Tracking: Operate the measurement framework that tracks tool&amp;nbsp;usage and adoption across the agency, partnering with finance partners to&amp;nbsp;quantify hours saved and financial impact.&lt;/li&gt;
