&lt;p&gt;As a Social Content Creator you’re obsessed with hands-on content creation and have a passion for innovation and creative craft. You have agency experience in creating short form social content for platforms like TikTok and Instagram using your strong editing and motion graphics skills. You will also bring a knack for ideation, strategic know-how, and a collaborative mindset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires someone who is organized, creative, and energized by making great work, whether that be concepting in partnership with the broader team, or picking up a camera and shooting/editing a piece of content yourself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will help shape the future of social media advertising for one of the world&#39;s most iconic and forward-thinking tech brands with revolutionary software solutions that empower creativity and productivity across the globe.&lt;/p&gt;
